        <updateDate>2021-04-29T04:03:21Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>American Flag Production Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill subjects a person to a fine if the person purchases a U.S. flag that is not 100% domestically made. Federal agencies are prohibited from purchasing such a flag.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
